Interface Dispatcher

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    public interface Dispatcher
extends CommandCallable
    Executes a command based on user input.

      • getCommands

        Set<? extends CommandMapping> getCommands()
        Gets a list of commands. Each command, regardless of how many aliases it may have, will only appear once in the returned set.

        The returned collection cannot be modified.

        Returns:
        A list of registrations

        The returned collection cannot be modified.

        Returns:

      • getAliases

        Set<String> getAliases()
        Gets a list of all the command aliases, which includes the primary alias.

        A command may have more than one alias assigned to it. The returned collection cannot be modified.

        Returns:
        A list of aliases
